<h2>Join Ruby Together</h2>

<p>Membership in Ruby Together is available to any individual or corporation that uses the Ruby programming language as part of their work. Membership dues can be paid monthly or annually, with all dues going towards the operation of Ruby Together and the maintenance and development of the Ruby tools and services you use every day.</p>

